data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bedroom, 2 and half bath, turn key ready home nestled in the desirable community of Poinciana. This spacious and beautifully designed residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.    As you enter, you'll be immediately impressed by the open and airy floor plan, flooded with natural light. The expansive living room provides ample space for relaxation and entertaining. Adjacent to the living room is a formal dining area, perfect for hosting dinner parties or enjoying family meals.    Upstairs, you'll find a spacious master bedroom suite, complete with a walk-in closet and a luxurious, modern bathroom. Three additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for family members or guests, all featuring ample closet space and windows that fill the rooms with natural light. An additional full bathroom provides convenience and comfort.     The backyard is a true retreat, boasting a spacious patio area that's perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Enjoy having company surrounding the fire pit with friends and family, or simply unwind and soak up the warm Florida sunshine in your private oasis that is FULLY FENCED.     This Poinciana gem is located in a family-friendly neighborhood, close to parks, schools, and shopping centers. With easy access to major highways, you'll have quick and convenient commuting options to nearby Orlando and other popular destinations. Don't miss the opportunity to make this magnificent 4 bedroom home yours.
